  "2370000": {
    "name": "Lumines Arise",
    "steam_appid": 2370000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款经典益智游戏《Lumines》的全新演绎版由《Tetris® Effect: Connected》原班人马倾力打造，将带给你极度上瘾的震撼体验——声音会贯穿你的身体、思维以及你放下的每一块方块，触发与强劲节拍同步的炫目视觉效果，伴随着风格多元的魔性配乐律动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越30多个有着各种感官共鸣奇境的关卡，从郁郁葱葱的丛林，到喧嚣热闹的东京街头，再到更加超现实的奇幻场景。利用全新的“Burst”机制来匹配方块、创造疯狂连击。除此之外，你还可以畅玩多种其他单人游戏模式和挑战，或者在在线多人游戏模式中与好友或陌生人一决高下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是想兴奋还是想冷静，无论你是这个系列的新手还是老玩家，无论你打算花上一个小时来大杀四方还是只有短短的五分钟，无论你是想独自游玩、与好友同乐还是想挑战陌生人，也无论你是想尝试VR模式还是震撼的4K画质，《Lumines Arise》都是你不可错过的终极益智游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法简单但深度十足</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/d15d5131ba264e7131ec0621c74e085d.poster.avif?t=1771547584\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/d15d5131ba264e7131ec0621c74e085d.webm?t=1771547584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/d15d5131ba264e7131ec0621c74e085d.mp4?t=1771547584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Lumines Arise》是一款非常容易上手但难于精通的游戏。玩家需要操控有着两种颜色的2×2方块，在这些方块从屏幕顶部落下后，玩家需要用它们拼出由单一颜色/类型方块组成的正方形。一条时间线会随着音乐的节拍横扫整个游戏区域，消除已完成的正方形并为玩家计分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >踏上奇妙旅程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/5ecb895b9de50e14b757a267d582841d.poster.avif?t=1771547584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/5ecb895b9de50e14b757a267d582841d.webm?t=1771547584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/5ecb895b9de50e14b757a267d582841d.mp4?t=1771547584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在有着超过30个关卡的单人游戏旅程中，每一站都会唤起不同且复杂的情绪反应。从郁郁葱葱的丛林、充满生机的海洋、随时准备出击的蛇群，到更具电子感的前沿世界，例如喧嚣的东京街头和无尽辽阔的外太空。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >充分利用Burst功能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/d90fee17384bbce4fc75210f8b175420.poster.avif?t=1771547584\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/d90fee17384bbce4fc75210f8b175420.webm?t=1771547584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/d90fee17384bbce4fc75210f8b175420.mp4?t=1771547584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >触发全新的“Burst”机制来阻止匹配好的正方形被清除，在时间耗尽之前把它堆砌得尽可能大。当时间线重新开始清扫时，你就可以享受满屏连锁清除、分数飙升不停的视觉盛宴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >展现自我</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/4462a9f3db8287171af1bc830d2e096a.poster.avif?t=1771547584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/4462a9f3db8287171af1bc830d2e096a.webm?t=1771547584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/4462a9f3db8287171af1bc830d2e096a.mp4?t=1771547584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用此系列史上最丰富的选项来自定义你的玩家头像。这是在开始游戏之旅时展示你个性与风格的最佳方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >戴上耳机，沉浸其中</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/5bd1b1bf7f027fc38da6e03b947f714e.poster.avif?t=1771547584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/5bd1b1bf7f027fc38da6e03b947f714e.webm?t=1771547584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370000/extras/5bd1b1bf7f027fc38da6e03b947f714e.mp4?t=1771547584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由备受赞誉的《Tetris Effect: Connected》和《Rez Infinite’s Area X》作曲家Hydelic倾力打造的震撼配乐，将把你带到沉浸式体验的新高度。戴上你最爱的耳机，尽情感受每一段旋律的律动。你还可以使用播放列表功能，自由组合喜爱的关卡与音乐或营造特定的游戏氛围。</p>",
